org.osate.xtext.aadl2.agcl.analysis.verifiers

Interface ModelCheckerInput

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    NuSMVInput
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ModelCheckerInputImpl, NuSMVInputImpl

    public interface ModelCheckerInput
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Model Checker Input'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Specification
    • Output
    • Verification Unit

    See Also:
    VerifiersPackage.getModelCheckerInput()
